## Data Processing Summary for Google Play

**Data Collected:**
- Email address (for authentication and account management)
- Name (for personalization)
- User-generated content (educational materials, responses)
- Chat history (for user access to past interactions)
- Feedback data (for service improvement)

**Data Usage:**
- Authentication and account management
- Providing personalized educational content
- Maintaining chat history for user reference
- Service improvement based on feedback

**Data Sharing:**
- No data is sold to third parties
- Google SSO provider receives authentication requests only
- No personal information is shared with other third parties

**Security:**
- Industry-standard encryption and security measures
- Secure storage of user data
- Regular security audits and updates
